# llz local credential cache — NEVER commit. Holds the Linode PAT, GitHub PATs,
# and the OBJ state key `llz tokens` gathers (mode 0600). `llz` reads it locally
# and pushes the secrets to the infra-<env> GitHub Environment; the files stay here.
.llz/

# Terraform working dirs + state. State lives in the remote OBJ backend, never in
# git; the plugin cache + plans are local build artifacts.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
